Ps in terms of power saving and resource\nutilization up to 88.5% and 21.12% respectively. In addition, the OM-FNN\npredictor shows better accuracy, lesser time and space complexity over a\ntraditional single-input and single-output feed-forward neural network\npredictor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Dec 2022 19:15:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-06"}
