PS\ncoordination of hot-air balloons and terrestrial base-stations for\ndemocratizing connectivity and empowering the digital inclusion framework.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Dec 2022 06:14:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-06"}
