e current and upcoming GW\ndetectors will soon become an excellent complement to the existing SETI\nefforts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Dec 2022 07:05:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 24 Dec 2022 17:35:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-27"}
