 masses and demonstrate that the extra lowest state depends strongly on\nthe pion mass. This suggests that the ground state of the scalar glueball has a\nlarge quark content, possibly representing the decay of a glueball to two\npions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Dec 2022 07:50:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-06"}
